==English==
===Noun===
'''mil'''
#a unit of [[angular]] measurement equal to 1/6400 of a complete circle. At 1000 metres one mil subtends one metre.
#a unit of measurement equal to 1/1000 of an [[inch]], usually usually used for thin objects, such as sheets of plastic.

